    <div class="full-width-cointainer">
      <div class="banner-bk">
	<img class="banner-img" src="http://img59.imageshack.us/img59/2539/2jyz.jpg" width="1349px" height="340px">
      </div>

      <!--CONTAINER-->
      <div class="cointainer">

	<!--PITCH-->
	<div class="row-fluid pitch">
          <div class="span5 offset1 video">
            <img src="http://img843.imageshack.us/img843/7472/l2ne.jpg" alt="Space for video" width="540" height="300">
          </div>

	  <!--ACTIONS-->
          <div class="span5 actions" ng-controller="OrdersCtrl">
            <div class="row-fluid">
              <div class="span8 offset2">
                <div class="row-fluid statistics">
                  <div ng-show="!error">
                    <div class="span4">
                      <div class="linediv-l">
			<h3>{{num_orders}}</h3> <p>backers</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="span4">
                      <div class="linediv-c">
			<h3>{{total_funded}}</h3> <p>of {{target}} <span class="currency">{{unit_symbol}}</span></p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="span4">
                      <div class="linediv-r">
			<h3>{{days_left}}</h3> <p>days left</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
		  </div>
		  <div ng-show="error">
                    <h3>{{error}}</h3>
		  </div>
		</div>
              </div>
              <div class="row-fluid" ng-show="!error">
		<div class="span10 offset1">
		  <!-- Bootstrap progress bar -->
		  <div class="thermometer progress active">
		    <div class="bar bar-success" ng-style="{'width': percentage_funded+'%'}"></div>
		    <div class="bar bar-warning" ng-style="{'width': (100-percentage_funded)+'%'}"></div>
		  </div>
		</div>
              </div>
              <div class="row-fluid">
		<div class="span6 offset3 order">
		  <a class="coinbase-button" 
                     data-button-style="custom_large" 
                     data-button-text="Preorder with Bitcoin" 
                     data-custom="Finished order"
                     data-code="<%= coinbase_preorder_data_code %>" 
                     href="https://coinbase.com/checkouts/<%= coinbase_preorder_data_code %>">Preorder with Bitcoin</a>
		</div>
              </div>
              <div class="row-fluid">
		<div class="span8 offset2 social">
		  <!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->
		  <div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style">
		    <a class="addthis_button_tweet" tw:via="<%= twitter_username %>" tw:text="<%= twitter_tweet %>"></a>
		  </div>
		  <script type="text/javascript" src="//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js#pubid=xa-5214a5fe5dbdc2b4"></script>
		  <!-- AddThis Button END -->
		</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
	</div><!--End of PITCH-->

	<!--MARKETING COPY-->
        <div class="row-fluid section1">
          <div class="span5 offset1 asset">
            <img src="http://img14.imageshack.us/img14/7455/xjez.jpg" alt="Creating profile" width="540" height="300" />
          </div>
          <div class="span5 copy">
            <p>
	      When people get older the exercise becomes non-existent or a rare activity only practiced by a few, despite well-known facts that regular physical activity has many health and lifestyle benefits. People with active lifestyle feel healthier and are less likely to suffer from heart disease, stroke, cancer or diabetes. If you want to get healthier and stay fit <span class="name">activfits</span> helps you find a perfect training program, a perfect fit to enhance your daily life and overall health, whether it is outside walks, swimming, jogging, Tai Chi or exercising whilst sitting on the chair.
            </p>
          </div>
	</div><!--End of section1-->

	<div class="row-fluid section2">
          <div class="span5 offset1 copy copy-right">
            <h2>WHAT IS <span class="name">ACTIVFITS?</span></h2>
	    <p>
              We all know that exercising helps us to enjoy energetic independent life, but <span class="name">activfits</span> helps you track your sports activities, improve with professional help, make new acquaintances and be a part of internet community. It is a source for fitness and health that is created to suit the needs of the elderly. You just have to set your preferences and a personal training program will be generated, with lots of recommendations, exercising videos and access to training, nutrition and many other professionals. Everyone is also encouraged to look for exercise buddies, organize sports and health events and share stories.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="span5 asset">
            <img src="http://img546.imageshack.us/img546/6990/3krk.jpg" alt="Recommendations" width="540" height="300">
          </div>
	</div><!--End of section2-->

	<div class="row-fluid section3">
          <div class="span5 offset1 asset">
              <img src="http://img194.imageshack.us/img194/7284/orhl.jpg" alt="Tracking app" width="540" height="300">
          </div>
          <div class="span5 copy">
            <h2>HOW DOES IT WORK?</h2>
        <p>Just create an account, download our health tracking apps or sync other tracking devices with our website. To get personalized training suggestions you have to take a test and answer a few simple questions like: "How often would you like to exercise?". All users get access to articles about health and fitness in older age, suggestions about exercise rutines and nutrition. You will be able to upload daily information from tracking devises and set personal goals. Data will be analysed and saved to help track the progress of your active life: performance, weight, heart rate, etc. You will also get recommendations on how to improve. Premium users will get access to hundreds of videos and exercise programs specialy created for elders. 
          </div>
        </div><!--end of section3-->
        
        <div class="row-fluid section4">
          <div class="span10 offset1">
            <h2>INTERESTED?</h2>
            <p>Help us kickstart <span class="name">activfits</span>! Currently we are working very hard to make this idea become a reality and any contribution will be highly appreciated. At the moment you can support us through Bitcoin and get a free Activfits membership or share our idea on Twitter and we will send you a massive hug! If you have any questions or suggestions on how we could improve our product, please don't hesitate and contact us at hello@activfits.com</p>
            </div>
        </div><!--end of section4-->

	<!--FAQ-->
	<div class="row-fluid faq">
          <div class ="span10 offset1">
            <h3>FAQ</h3>
            <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">
            
              <div class="accordion-group">
                <div class="accordion-heading">
                  <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseOne">
